A loving son and husband
David Buchler

To Honour A Dear Father
PHILIP BUCHLER
He Spent Many Happy Hours In This Sunny Garden
A Philosopher, Furrier, Worked in Mayfair & Died Too Soon
May 6th 1905 - June 23rd 1972"Ţ
